# Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials → OAuth client ID (Web application).
# Authorized JavaScript origins: e.g. http://localhost:5173 and your production URL.
# Authorized redirect URIs (required for phone/small-screen Google sign-in):
#   http://localhost:5173/google-signin-callback
#   https://YOUR-PRODUCTION-DOMAIN/google-signin-callback
# Put your real Client ID in .env (this file is only a template — do not commit secrets).
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
